      "review_summary": "This PR removes package exclusions for `ssrf-runtime-internal`, adds it to package exports, removes it from private local-only SDK subpaths, and raises Plugin SDK surface-report budgets.\n\nPR surface: Config +2, Other 0. Total +2 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level. Current main and `v2026.6.10` have Browser/Ollama imports from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/ssrf-runtime-internal` while package metadata excludes and does not export that subpath; contributor terminal proof shows `openclaw browser status` succeeds after this branch.",
